nd people skills; positive attitude and team player Strong prior Knowledge of Media Tools and reporting systems is a plus Please note this position is on site only Compensation & Benefits Salary commensurate with experience Health Benefits Paid Time Off Fun, energizing work environment Job Type: Full-time Pay: $60,000.00 - $80,000.00 per year Experience: DRTV media buying: 2 years (Preferred) Additional Compensation: Bonuses Work Location: One location Schedule: Monday to Friday Company's website: spindle360.com "
